snippet.title: The Sad Fate of One Week at Flumpty's [Unofficial Reupload]
snippet.description:
As of October 31st 2021, One Night at Flumpty's 3 has been released and effectively replaced this game. Download here: https://gamejolt.com/games/onaf3/529078

This is a reupload from Jonochrome's channel, which you can find here: https://www.youtube.com/user/Jonochrome
This was reuploaded for anyone who was curious as to what Jonochrome had to say in the video.
